description: [``botocore``] This release adds Hybridcast as an available profile option for Dash Origin Endpoints.
[``botocore``] Documentation updates for Multi-AZ DB clusters.
[``botocore``] Add support for GP3 and IO2 volume types. Add bootMode to LaunchConfiguration object (and as a parameter to UpdateLaunchConfigurationRequest).

[``botocore``] Adds operation for custom plugin deletion (DeleteCustomPlugin) and adds new StateDescription field to DescribeCustomPlugin and DescribeConnector responses to return errors from asynchronous resource creation.
